action.description: The action to display in the card header.
action.description_zh: 要在卡头中显示的操作。

avatar.description_zh: 要显示的 Avatar 元素。

classes.description: Override or extend the styles applied to the component.See CSS classes API below for more details.
classes.description_zh: 覆盖或扩展应用于组件的样式。有关详细信息，请参阅下面的 CSS 类 API。

component.description: The component used for the root node. Either a string to use a HTML element or a component.
component.description_zh: 用于根节点的组件。使用 HTML 元素或组件的字符串。

disableTypography.description: If true, subheader and title won't be wrapped by a Typography component. This can be useful to render an alternative Typography variant by wrapping the title text, and optional subheader text with the Typography component.
disableTypography.description_zh: 如果为 true，则 subheader 和 title 不会由 Typography 组件包装。这对于通过包装标题文本和带有 Typography 组件的可选副标题文本来呈现替代 Typography 变体非常有用。

subheaderTypographyProps.description: These props will be forwarded to the subheader (as long as disableTypography is not true).
subheaderTypographyProps.description_zh: 这些道具将被转发到子标题（只要 disableTypography 不为 true）。

sx.description: The system prop that allows defining system overrides as well as additional CSS styles.See the `sx` page for more details.
sx.description_zh: 允许定义系统覆盖以及其他 CSS 样式的系统属性。有关更多详细信息，请参阅“sx”页面。

titleTypographyProps.description: These props will be forwarded to the title (as long as disableTypography is not true).
titleTypographyProps.description_zh: 这些道具将被转发到标题中（只要 disableTypography 不为 true）。
